---
title: Speaking
permalink: /talks/
layout: base
skip_footer: false
---
<div class="min-h-screen flex flex-col w-full">
  <%= render "header", page: resource, menu: site.data.menu %>

  <main class="flex-auto">
    <!-- Hero (simplified) -->
    <section class="relative py-20 md:py-32 overflow-hidden">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 overflow-hidden pointer-events-none">
        <div class="absolute -top-1/4 -right-1/4 w-[600px] h-[600px] bg-gradient-to-br from-accent-200/20 to-transparent rounded-full blur-3xl dark:from-accent-900/10"></div>
      </div>

      <div class="relative w-full max-w-[90rem] mx-auto px-6 md:px-12">
        <div class="max-w-4xl">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-8">
            <div class="w-12 h-0.5 bg-accent-500"></div>
            <span class="text-sm font-mono uppercase tracking-widest text-accent-600 dark:text-accent-400">Speaking</span>
          </div>

          <h1 class="font-serif text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-semibold text-stone-900 dark:text-stone-100 leading-[1.15] tracking-tight mb-8">
            I don't speak often,<br class="hidden sm:block" />
            but when I do it's about<br class="hidden lg:block" />
            <span class="text-accent-600 dark:text-accent-400">what actually works.</span>
          </h1>

          <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-stone-600 dark:text-stone-400 leading-relaxed max-w-2xl">
            Hard-won lessons from a decade of building and leading engineering teams. No frameworks for frameworks' sake—just the stuff that's made a real difference.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Philosophy Section -->
    <section class="py-20 md:py-28 bg-stone-900 dark:bg-stone-950">
      <div class="w-full max-w-[90rem] mx-auto px-6 md:px-12">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-16">
          <div class="w-16 h-0.5 bg-accent-500"></div>
          <h2 class="text-sm font-mono uppercase tracking-widest text-stone-500">What I Talk About</h2>
        </div>

        <div class="grid gap-16 md:gap-20 max-w-4xl">
          <!-- High-Trust Teams -->
          <div class="group">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-6">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-14 h-14 rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-br from-brand-500 to-brand-700 flex items-center justify-center shadow-lg shadow-brand-500/20">
                <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M15 19.128a9.38 9.38 0 002.625.372 9.337 9.337 0 004.121-.952 4.125 4.125 0 00-7.533-2.493M15 19.128v-.003c0-1.113-.285-2.16-.786-3.07M15 19.128v.106A12.318 12.318 0 018.624 21c-2.331 0-4.512-.645-6.374-1.766l-.001-.109a6.375 6.375 0 0111.964-3.07M12 6.375a3.375 3.375 0 11-6.75 0 3.375 3.375 0 016.75 0zm8.25 2.25a2.625 2.625 0 11-5.25 0 2.625 2.625 0 015.25 0z" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">
                  High-Trust Teams
                </h3>
                <p class="text-lg text-brand-400 mb-4">The foundation of everything.</p>
                <p class="text-stone-400 leading-relaxed">
                  Trust is the multiplier. Teams that have it move faster, take bigger swings, and recover from failure with grace. I share how to build it intentionally—through authenticity, psychological safety, and the small daily choices that compound.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Directed Chaos -->
          <div class="group">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-6">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-14 h-14 rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-500 to-emerald-700 flex items-center justify-center shadow-lg shadow-emerald-500/20">
                <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3.75 13.5l10.5-11.25L12 10.5h8.25L9.75 21.75 12 13.5H3.75z" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">
                  Directed Chaos
                </h3>
                <p class="text-lg text-emerald-400 mb-4">Embracing turbulence over comfort.</p>
                <p class="text-stone-400 leading-relaxed">
                  Most leaders optimize for stability. I optimize for resilience. Layoffs, pivots, reorgs—not avoiding chaos, but harnessing it. Comfort is where growth goes to die.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- High-Agency Leadership -->
          <div class="group">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-6">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-14 h-14 rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-br from-accent-500 to-accent-700 flex items-center justify-center shadow-lg shadow-accent-500/20">
                <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M15.59 14.37a6 6 0 01-5.84 7.38v-4.8m5.84-2.58a14.98 14.98 0 006.16-12.12A14.98 14.98 0 009.631 8.41m5.96 5.96a14.926 14.926 0 01-5.841 2.58m-.119-8.54a6 6 0 00-7.381 5.84h4.8m2.581-5.84a14.927 14.927 0 00-2.58 5.84m2.699 2.7c-.103.021-.207.041-.311.06a15.09 15.09 0 01-2.448-2.448 14.9 14.9 0 01.06-.312m-2.24 2.39a4.493 4.493 0 00-1.757 4.306 4.493 4.493 0 004.306-1.758M16.5 9a1.5 1.5 0 11-3 0 1.5 1.5 0 013 0z" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">
                  High-Agency Leadership
                </h3>
                <p class="text-lg text-accent-400 mb-4">Building teams that don't need you.</p>
                <p class="text-stone-400 leading-relaxed">
                  The best thing you can build is a team that doesn't need you. Hold people to a bar they thought was impossible, then watch them clear it. Most people deeply underestimate themselves—your job is to help them see what they're capable of.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Past Speaking -->
    <% all_talks = collections.talks.resources.sort_by { |t| -t.data.year } %>
    <% if all_talks.any? %>
      <section class="py-20 md:py-28">
        <div class="w-full max-w-[90rem] mx-auto px-6 md:px-12">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-12">
            <div class="w-16 h-0.5 bg-stone-300 dark:bg-stone-700"></div>
            <h2 class="text-sm font-mono uppercase tracking-widest text-stone-500 dark:text-stone-500">Past Speaking</h2>
          </div>

          <div class="max-w-4xl space-y-0">
            <% all_talks.each do |talk| %>
              <div class="group flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-baseline gap-2 sm:gap-8 py-5 border-b border-stone-200 dark:border-stone-800">
                <span class="text-sm font-mono text-stone-400 dark:text-stone-600 tabular-nums w-12"><%= talk.data.year %></span>
                <div class="flex-1 min-w-0">
                  <a href="<%= talk.relative_url %>" class="font-semibold text-stone-900 dark:text-stone-100 hover:text-accent-600 dark:hover:text-accent-400 transition-colors">
                    <%= talk.data.title %>
                  </a>
                  <span class="text-stone-500 dark:text-stone-500"> · <%= talk.data.event %></span>
                  <% if talk.data.type == "workshop" %>
                    <span class="ml-2 px-2 py-0.5 text-xs font-medium uppercase tracking-wider bg-stone-100 dark:bg-stone-800 text-stone-500 dark:text-stone-400 rounded">Workshop</span>
                  <% end %>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-center gap-4 text-sm shrink-0">
                  <% if talk.data.video_url %>
                    <a href="<%= talk.data.video_url %>" class="text-stone-500 hover:text-accent-600 dark:hover:text-accent-400 transition-colors" rel="external" target="_blank">Video</a>
                  <% end %>
                  <% if talk.data.slides_url %>
                    <a href="<%= talk.data.slides_url %>" class="text-stone-500 hover:text-accent-600 dark:hover:text-accent-400 transition-colors" rel="external" target="_blank">Slides</a>
                  <% end %>
                </div>
              </div>
            <% end %>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    <% end %>

    <!-- Speaking CTA -->
    <section class="relative py-24 md:py-32 overflow-hidden">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-accent-600 via-accent-700 to-stone-900">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[url('data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20width%3D%2260%22%20height%3D%2260%22%20viewBox%3D%220%200%2060%2060%22%20xmlns%3D%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F2000%2Fsvg%22%3E%3Cg%20fill%3D%22none%22%20fill-rule%3D%22evenodd%22%3E%3Cg%20fill%3D%22%23ffffff%22%20fill-opacity%3D%220.05%22%3E%3Cpath%20d%3D%22M36%2034v-4h-2v4h-4v2h4v4h2v-4h4v-2h-4zm0-30V0h-2v4h-4v2h4v4h2V6h4V4h-4zM6%2034v-4H4v4H0v2h4v4h2v-4h4v-2H6zM6%204V0H4v4H0v2h4v4h2V6h4V4H6z%22%2F%3E%3C%2Fg%3E%3C%2Fg%3E%3C%2Fsvg%3E')] opacity-30"></div>
      </div>

      <div class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/4 -translate-y-1/2 w-64 h-64 bg-white/5 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
      <div class="absolute top-1/2 right-1/4 -translate-y-1/2 w-96 h-96 bg-brand-500/10 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>

      <div class="relative w-full max-w-[90rem] mx-auto px-6 md:px-12">
        <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
          <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-semibold text-white mb-6">
            Let's talk about<br class="hidden sm:block" /> <em class="text-accent-200">what actually works</em>
          </h2>
          <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-white/70 max-w-xl mx-auto mb-10">
            If you're organizing a conference, podcast, or workshop and think my perspective would resonate with your audience—I'd love to hear from you.
          </p>

          <a href="mailto:jesse@jcmcginnis.com" class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 px-10 py-5 bg-white hover:bg-stone-100 text-stone-900 text-lg font-bold rounded-full transition-all hover:scale-105 shadow-2xl">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3 8l7.89 5.26a2 2 0 002.22 0L21 8M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z" />
            </svg>
            Get in touch
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <%= render "footer" %>
</div>
